projects.name: Newell Auto Service
projects.description: A full-featured static SPA developed for a local mobile automotive repair service. Built with React, this webpage features direct email communication.

projects.name: Mars Weather Report
projects.description: Ever wonder how cold Mars is right now? This web app brings that very information to you and more. This captures data from the InSight Rover on Mars and parses it into a readable UI. Built from scratch with React.JS.

projects.name: Rattle Scan
projects.description: This web app is for finding and reporting rattlesnake sightings. Other users can use this information to avoid potentially dangerous areas. Skills: JavaScript, HTML, CSS, Google Maps API.

projects.name: Diabetic-Recipe Twitter Bot
projects.description: Built with Node, this searches Twitter for posts with different Diabetic-related recipes and meals. This app then retweets the collected posts for users to easily find.
